'''Niwemwiza Marie Anne''' ni umunyarwandakazi uri mu itangazamakuru kuva muri Mutarama 2008 atangirira kuri [https://www.radiomaria.rw/ radio maria Rwanda], akomereza umwuga  w' itangazamakuru ahandi akaba amaze Imyaka 14.<ref>https://www.ktradio.rw/2018/08/24/anne-marie-niwemwiza/</ref>

== UBUZIMA BWITE ==
Niwemwiza Marie Anne ni umugore ufite abana 2, aho umugabo we nawe ari umunyamakurukuri wa RBA ([https://www.rba.co.rw/radio Rwanda Broadcasting Agency]). <ref>https://www.bwiza.com/?Abanyamakuru-Niwemwiza-na-Isheja-bibarutse-ubuheta</ref> Anne Ukora itangazamakuru nk'umwuga aho atanga ibitekerezo bivugira rubanda.  "Iki ni ikimenyetso cy'uko niyemeje gukomera ku bunyarwanda nk'igihango mfitanye n'igihugu n'urungano" iryo ni rimwe mu ijmabo yavuze.<ref>https://nitter.net/Annemwiza</ref><ref>https://kiny.taarifa.rw/ingabire-immaculee-a-marie-niwemwiza-miss-jolly-hari-icyo-bavuga-kuri-bridal-shower/</ref>

=== Ibihembo yabonye ===
'''Niwemwiza Marie Anne''' umaze imyaka mwinshi ari umunyamakuru kuri [https://onlineradiobox.com/rw/kt/ KT Radio] akora ikiganiro "Ubyumva ute", aho yegukanye igihembo ku kiganiro gikorwa neza cya Radio, cyatanzwe n'ishyirahamwe ry'abanyamkuru hizihizwa umunsi w'itangazamakuru. Anne kandi azwi ku mbuga nkoranyambaga nka twitter ku izina rya @annemwiza, aho akurikirwa n'abantu barenga 40,000.<ref>http://www.agasaro.com/spip.php?article4382</ref>

